    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Earth has been discovered by aliens! But don’t worry, they’re nice aliens. Actually, it’s been so long since anybody in the Pan Galactic Tourist Federation has had anywhere new to go, they’re actually kind of bored aliens.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as Cosmo on their first ever field assignment to document the cultures, and take samples of the lifeforms of the Earth so it can be approved as a brand new PGTF tourist destination. Accompanied by their assistant Pea, they’re excited to discover everything there is to be discovered on this wonderful little blue ball.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The world is your playground!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314190/extras/22af0d1193897f18be4e75a9b1d0a918.poster.avif?t=1744268073\" width=600 height=148 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314190/extras/22af0d1193897f18be4e75a9b1d0a918.webm?t=1744268073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314190/extras/22af0d1193897f18be4e75a9b1d0a918.mp4?t=1744268073\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solo adventure with 2/3 hours of play time</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 UFO beams to capture, throw, draw, and grow</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Exploration!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314190/extras/02435b508ea03400ff30f6071858bd1e.poster.avif?t=1744268073\" width=600 height=148 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314190/extras/02435b508ea03400ff30f6071858bd1e.webm?t=1744268073\" 